The Master of KIN (c) 1988 Du Tech.

A sideways scrolling beat-em-up game.

In the time of the gods, evil roamed free in the lands. Zorg &apos;The Master of Kin&apos;, took his wife to temple and before kissing her, suddenly the evil sorcerer Zangar came and invaded the place and took his wife kidnapped towards his castle. The knight  Zorg begins his quest in the outlands of the Kin domain to rescue his wife from the enemy hands.

